<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.7.7">
<l>kaṟuttuk kañcaṉai yañcamu ṉintāy kārvaṇ ṇākaṭal pōloḷi vaṇṇā</l>
<l>viṟuttiṭ ṭāṉviṭai yēḻumuṉ veṉṟā yentā yantara mēḻumu ṉāṉāy</l>
<l>poṟuttuk koṇṭirun tālpoṟuk koṇāp pōka mēnukar vāṉpukun taivar</l>
<l>aṟuttut tiṉṟiṭa vañciniṉ ṉaṭaintē ṉaḻuntūr mēlticai niṉṟavam māṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who, being angry, raged so that angry Kaṁsa feared, cloud-colored one,</l>
<l rend="indent">you the hue of splendor like the sea,</l>
<l>You who once conquered seven bulls, completely crushing [them], my father,</l>
<l rend="indent">you who long ago became the seven heavens,</l>
<l>Fearing that, if [I] keep being tolerant, the five senses, surging in [me]</l>
<l rend="indent">to relish pleasures for which tolerance is not possible,</l>
<l>Tormenting [me], will completely grind [me] down,</l>
<l rend="indent">I resorted to you, lord who stands at the west side of Aḻuntūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
